In a large microwave safe bowl, heat margarine and marshmallows at HIGH for 3 minutes, stirring after 2 minutes. Stir in vanilla. Stir in KELLOGG'S* RICE KRISPIES* cereal until well coated. Using 1/4 cup measure and buttered hands, shape cereal mixture into 7cm balls. Using icing to attach two balls together to form bunny body and head. Use icing, attach paper bunny ears and licorice for whiskers. Make eyes, mouth, and tail.